```class Solution {
    public boolean hasAlternatingBits(int n) {
        int prevBit = n & 1;
        while ((n >>= 1) > 0) {
            int currBit = n & 1;
            if (prevBit == currBit) return false;
            prevBit = currBit;
        }
        return true;
    }
}```
